    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《BZZZT》是一款快节奏的“跑-跳-冲”平台跳跃游戏，结合了怀旧风的像素画面和现代化的游戏设计。几乎完全由一位开发者——Karel Matejka，又名Ko.dll——独立完成，并献与我们心爱的经典游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款细节满满的像素精确平台跳跃游戏灵感来自于80年代的技术革命，能够带您一路回溯时光，体验新鲜奇异的冒险、游历设计精妙的关卡、解锁形形色色的技能、投身紧张刺激的BOSS战！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《BZZZT》简述</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据自身平台跳跃经验来选择不同的难度等级，可休闲可硬核。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受极度精准且符合直觉，随时随地且随心所欲的操控手感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在激动人心的时长挑战中挑战自己的极限。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全球或好友排行榜中与其他玩家决一高下。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验丰富的环境因素和不断变化的游戏机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一路克服困难不断精进，用适合自己的游玩风格做好应对高强度BOSS战的准备。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可供玩家选择的永久死亡模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由制作了Rytmik Ultimate/Studio的Martin Linda所编写的优美复古音乐将让您沉浸其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/4da324ffa5aaa981ccdb6f607c2d5acd.poster.avif?t=1750557220\" width=610 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/4da324ffa5aaa981ccdb6f607c2d5acd.webm?t=1750557220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/4da324ffa5aaa981ccdb6f607c2d5acd.mp4?t=1750557220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《BZZZT》会将您带至……4096年</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一所绝密实验室中，艾米丽博士和世界闻名的诺威伯特教授正在推进一个高度机密项目。一个带有强大AI的个性化小机器人最终成为了他们的合作与智慧所碰撞出的火花！虽然比普通的家用面包机大不了多少，但ZX8000的技巧足以克服一次次的平台挑战，逐步拯救全世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/4320ac234db1f48a89d681c512f3e661.poster.avif?t=1750557220\" width=610 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/4320ac234db1f48a89d681c512f3e661.webm?t=1750557220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/4320ac234db1f48a89d681c512f3e661.mp4?t=1750557220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们当然不能纵容黑暗势力统治《BZZZT》的世界。邪恶的疯狂科学家巴尔伯特已经整装待发，在寻得黑暗、恶念和疯狂的完美平衡后就向毫无准备的世界启用自己的邪恶计划。哇哈哈哈哈哈！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/99ec46530cabc967ee43c3c40e0b0026.poster.avif?t=1750557220\" width=610 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/99ec46530cabc967ee43c3c40e0b0026.webm?t=1750557220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/99ec46530cabc967ee43c3c40e0b0026.mp4?t=1750557220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那，您还在等什么呢？拿上您的手柄或键盘，指引ZX8000完成任务，挫败巴尔伯特的邪恶计划吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为拯救世界的小机器人吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293170/extras/e46da156f274b1d2ea8c3bc29e1fd272.avif?t=1750557220\" width=600 height=557 /></span></p>",
